  <div class="prose" data-reveal="2" style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">
    <p class="lede" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      This is a small, quiet place I keep for myself — and for anyone
      who wanders in.
    </p>

    <p>
      I made this room as somewhere to think out loud without the noise.
      It's part journal, part workshop, part window into the things I
      notice when the world goes still. Writing lives here, and the
      projects I've been slowly tending to, and whatever else feels
      worth setting down.
    </p>

    <p>
      I'm drawn to slow ideas, unfinished thoughts, and the space
      between things. If any of that resonates, you're welcome to stay
      a while.
    </p>

